snippet.title: Sicko Sanctum - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
After 7 months of on and off development, it's finally done. Sicko Sanctum is a score attack boomer shooter with certain spices of character action. In other words,  a Doom + Pacman that owns a Devil May Cry shirt. This is the sequel to Monolith of Foolery and the third and final title of the Millawar Saga.

Download here on itch.io dot com for FREE:
https://jake-stevenson.itch.io/sicko-sanctum
